'''琴蛙属'''(''Nidirana'' )，是[[无尾目|无尾目]][[蛙科|蛙科]]的一属动物。原为[[拇棘蛙屬|拇棘蛙屬]]（''Babina''）的异名，2017年重新恢复了该属的有效性，从拇棘蛙屬拆分出一部分物种到琴蛙属<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Lyu |first1=Zhi-Tong |last2=Zeng |first2=Zhao-Chi |last3=Wang |first3=Jian |last4=Lin |first4=Chao-Yu |last5=Liu |first5=Zu-Yao |last6=Wang |first6=Ying-Yong |title=Resurrection of genus Nidirana (Anura: Ranidae) and synonymizing N. caldwelli with N. adenopleura, with description of a new species from China |journal=Amphibia-Reptilia |date=2017-01-01 |volume=38 |issue=4 |pages=483–502 |doi=10.1163/15685381-00003130}}</ref>。

